{"tid":884233,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實M記今次只係打個和","createTime":"2018-10-31T12:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T12:26:13.000Z","uid":26931,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b25f6c3d5c8d45cee0ec82f86a03a701e8801824","tid":884233,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:15:23.000Z","msg":"大佬，四十蚊個包，連薯條同可樂，就可以食到謝霆鋒親自整既包，喂大佬，謝霆鋒喎，你以為係街邊啲二打六阿？佢既taste有幾好大家都知，有名你叫亞洲Gordon Edison&nbsp;Ramsay，而家佢每日要整成幾萬個包比你班老細，我uncle整左幾廿年包都同我講，謝霆鋒而家起碼要每朝凌晨3點起身開始整先得，如果唔賣貴啲仲得了既？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以話你班皇帝唔好再係度嫌三嫌四，我食過，入面啲肉醬味道香濃，煎蛋烚到好處，真係食得出係出自頂級廚師之手，問心，我覺得個質素起碼去到$300+既價位，先唔講食物成本，齋計謝霆鋒既心血，我覺得就已經值得食完再食，我而家就一日三餐都食，今晚諗住再買多兩個訓教前再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，先食為敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YkiBxHK_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYkiBxHK_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=b6099e2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"224423ebdae6b7da24abbdeebf933e157ca21e18","tid":884233,"uid":92,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"邊個係Gordon Ramsay?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1f990bc4b47732c0b66ebbb62fa5bb905ed066","tid":884233,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"仆街 成50蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你個燒味 完全係燒烤片噉解<br />\n<br />\n個包 多pat 嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杯嘢甜撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74491f763f34a99e2945f803bb9326c8ed0ad8f2","tid":884233,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re